Looking at the balance sheet, I can see:

1. The "Taxes Payable" line item has:
   - Initial amount: 0.00 on 2023-12-31
   - End amount: 290671.05 on 2024-01-28

This represents the tax liability that the company has accrued but not yet paid as of the reporting dates.

Therefore, the tax accrued but not yet paid is:
- Initial value: 0.00
- End value: 290671.05
